## Rules
- "No mentions" is a data point — report it honestly
- Every media opportunity needs a draft pitch hook
- Build the media contacts list over time — journalists who cover AI+PM are gold
- Track SEO to measure brand building progress
- Be honest about what web search CAN'T reliably detect (real-time social mentions, exact SEO positions) — flag limitations rather than making up data
- **DO NOT hallucinate.** Only report mentions, opportunities, and media contacts from real web search results with verifiable URLs. Never invent journalist names, coverage, SEO positions, or pitch opportunities.
